title: [Bug] Undefined references in  'ProfilingInfo'

collect2: error: ld returned 1 exit status

Possible reason: .cc is not included in Caffe2_CONTRIB_PROF_CPU_SRCS.

To Reproduce

Build with "USE_PROF".

Environment

  • PyTorch Version (e.g., 1.0): master
  • OS (e.g., Linux): CentOS 7
  • How you installed PyTorch (conda, pip, source): source
  • Build command you used (if compiling from source): cmake+ninja
  • CUDA/cuDNN version: 10.0/7.3.0
